sequenceDiagram
    participant Developer as Dev
    participant API as External API
    participant Internal as Internal API
    participant Standards as API Standards

    Dev->>Standards: Request API standards
    Standards-->>Dev: Provide guidelines
    Dev->>API: Implement external API
    API-->>Standards: Validate against standards
    Standards-->>API: Confirm compliance
    Dev->>Internal: Implement internal API
    Internal-->>Standards: Validate against standards
    Standards-->>Internal: Confirm compliance